BBC Plans to Cut Employee Total by One Quarter, Guardian Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-03-16T18:51:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/bbc-plans-to-cut-employee-total-by-one-quarter-guardian-reports.html
The British Broadcasting Corp. aims
to eliminate 25 percent of its workforce by 2016 to realize
savings necessitated by a six-year license-fee freeze, the
Guardian reported, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Simpson at 
 jsimpson12@bloomberg.net  